### Content & SEO Automation Templates

- [PATTERN] **Google Forms → AI blog pipeline**: Google Forms collects topic/keyword inputs → n8n webhook receives submission → Groq/Mistral generates SEO-optimised post → publishes to WordPress. Generalises to any form-driven content factory; swap LLM provider without changing flow structure. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

- [PATTERN] **Stale content detector**: Scheduled n8n workflow → fetch sitemap → for each URL: crawl page content → send to OpenAI with a freshness-scoring prompt → write results to Google Sheets (ContentAudit tab). Flag pages where score < threshold for manual review. Avoids crawling budget waste and preserves ranking signals on evergreen content. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

- [PATTERN] **Lead qualification + auto-response via OpenAI + Gmail**: Webhook or form trigger → OpenAI scores lead (ICP fit, urgency) and generates personalised reply → Gmail sends draft or auto-sends based on score threshold. Reduces first-response time to seconds; human reviews flagged edge cases only. Guard clause: wrap OpenAI call in error node — API failures must not silently drop leads. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

